# Do not do list
1) Do not use backticks (i.e. `cmd`). Use $(cmd) instead
2) Do not use [ .. ] in bash, only use in sh [1]

# notes
1) Consistenly use (( )) to test numbers or arithmetic, and [[ ]] to test strings or files

